1. *Obećala* je da će doći na naš događaj. (She promised that she would come to our event.) 
2. Ona se *obećala* da će biti uspešna. (She promised herself that she would be successful.) 
3. Ona je *obećala* da će mi pomoći. (She promised me that she would help me.) 
4. On je *obećao* da će biti tu za nas. (He promised that he would be there for us.) 
5. Oni su *obećali* da će doći na vreme. (They promised that they would come on time.)